{"tid":2295241,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國政府5個部門告知其僱員最快8周之內可接種輝瑞(PFE.US)或Moderna(MRNA.US)旗下疫苗","createTime":"2020-11-21T15:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T15:44:28.000Z","uid":6940,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9a62de7596a63e6fa66e56302731726c1b9fbee8","tid":2295241,"uid":6940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:22:36.000Z","msg":"美國已經有5個聯邦政府部門告知其僱員們，他們最快8周之內就可以接種輝瑞(<a href=\"http://PFE.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FPFE.US&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=2513fc21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">PFE.US</a>)或Moderna(<a href=\"http://MRNA.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMRNA.US&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=df86bd26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">MRNA.US</a>)研發的疫苗，其中就包括美國國務院那些年齡達到或超過70歲的外交人員。<br />\n<br />\n美國疾控中心(CDC)發佈&ldquo;過渡計劃&rdquo;，除了眾多衞生工作人員之外，那些必不可少的聯邦僱員也將是首批接種疫苗的美國人。具體接種時間將嚴重地取決於美國食品藥品管理局(FDA)能以多快的速度審批並授予前述兩家公司的疫苗以緊急使用授權(EUA)。<br />\n<br />\n截至週五收盤，輝瑞收漲1.41%，報36.7美元；Moderna收漲5.22%，報97.61美元。"},{"pid":"ba9d1b11796fad42c5c8eea0c40e60c933db0e3b","tid":2295241,"uid":383914,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G3sR48P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG3sR48P.gif&h=707a6def&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3CbjuAy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3CbjuAy.gif&h=f7184692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5K04FHi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5K04FHi.gif&h=fc8d52b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbRfNnn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbRfNnn.gif&h=7e201df3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e968bd55a6d9bddeaf8fd8684e2617031fb391eb","tid":2295241,"uid":90883,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":